decision_details:
- the proposal made by H.E. the President  in his capacity as the Minister of Highways, Ports and Shipping, to award the contracts for the rehabilitation of the following sections of roads as recommended by the Standing Cabinet Appointed Procurement Committee (SCAPC), was approved by the Cabinet:

* Narandeniya - Hakmana Road from 0 to 11.95 km;
* Ayagama - Egaloya Road from 0 to 23 km;
* Mawanella - Hemmathagama - Gampala Road from 0 to 26.00 km; and 
* Hatton - Maskeliya - Delhousie Road from 0 to 31.89 km
